+Following are the KVM-defined registers for x86:
+
+======================= ========= =============================================
+    Encoding            Register  Description
+======================= ========= =============================================
+  0x2030 0003 0000 0000 SSP       Shadow Stack Pointer
+======================= ========= =============================================
